1. Permission for Distribution:
   Distribution of modified or unmodified versions of the source code is permitted, including forks.

2. Prohibition on Closed-Source Use:
   Derivatives or versions of this work may not be distributed as closed source for profit without the explicit permission of the original creator.

3. Attribution:
   Any distribution must include proper attribution to the original creator.

4. Commercial Use:
   Commercial use of the source code or derivatives is permitted only in compliance with these terms.
